<br>
Well, things are different now. The higher in season ye gits, the margin o' difference gits wider and wider. Over time, yer AC, HP, Magic Resist, and higher skill caps surpass any other class by a significant amount. And soon whut wuz only a subtle difference that gave groups reason to PREFER us becomes an obvious and noticeable difference that gives groups reason to NEED us.<br>
<br>
